info.author: Spirent Communications plc
info.name: SpirentSLC
info.summary: The SpirentSLC package provides a session level control interface to all Spirent iTest sessions. iTest scripts that are exported to Python require this package to allow QuickCalls and command execution on all devices in a test bed. All response structures (raw, auto-mapped, and response mapped) are available as objects on which assertions can be performed for each step in a test case.
